* $B\\in[0,1]$: effective bandwidth (nodes\'d7health\'d7energy), capped.\
* Use $\\hat P$ for thresholds.\
\
## Adaptive Capacity\
\
$$\
A = w_N N + w_T S_T + w_S M_\{\\text\{SHI\}\},\\quad w_\\bullet\\ge0,\\,\\sum w=1\
$$\
\
* $N$: nutrient/energy headroom; $S_T$: tracer slack; $M_\{\\text\{SHI\}\}=\\max(0,\\text\{SHI\}-\\theta_\{\\text\{safe\}\})$.\
\
## Forecast Index\
\
$$\
F=\\frac\{P\}\{A\},\\quad F^\\ast=\\alpha F+(1-\\alpha)F^\\ast_\{t-1\}\\ (\\alpha\\in[0.2,0.6])\
$$\
