## SHI (composite, schematic)\
\
$$\
\\text\{SHI\}=1-\\big(\\alpha E_s+\\beta V_e+\\gamma D_t+\\delta(1-S_c)+\\phi_\{\\text\{soot/ash\}\}\\big)\
$$\
\
* $E_s$: sigil entropy; $V_e$: edge volatility; $D_t$: tracer divergence; $S_c$: SCUP coherence term.\
