## SCUP: Probability of Coherence Loss\
\
$$\
p_\{\\text\{loss\}\}=\\sigma\\!\\big(a F^\\ast + b \\hat P + c\\,\\Delta\\!\\text\{drift\} + d\\,\\bar\\tau - e A - f\\,\\text\{SHI\}\\big)\
$$\
\
* $\\Delta\\!\\text\{drift\}$: forecast vs realized drift (cosine distance).\
* $\\bar\\tau$: mean tension of hot edges.\
* $\\sigma(x)=\\frac\{1\}\{1+e^\{-x\}\}$.\
* Action if $p_\{\\text\{loss\}\}>\\theta$ (e.g., 0.7).\
